Steps to parse hackwiki db into Nethack Encyclopedia format

- grab snapshot of db from http://nethack.wikia.com/wiki/Special:Statistics

- create necessary dirs
    mkdir split compressed

- run parser:
    ruby parser.rb <full-path-to-mediawiki-snapshot>

- compress result:
    for file in `ls split` ; do
      gzip -c split/$file > compressed/$file.gz
    done

- link compressed to assets directory
    ln -s <project-path>/util/parser/compressed <project-path>/assets/encyclopedia
